description:
The Grappler was ranked 6th last year, and at the end of the season was a top tier wrestler. She has sound moves, and nice leg skills. She is a style point monster. Darling is a contender for this season championship.
The Green Machine is pound for pound the strongest wrestler we have. She is tiny but a ball of lighting. She has only one lost her at US. Give credit to Shannon for going giving up almost 40 lbs to a more experienced wrestler. What did she get for her troubles? Nearly fucked to death by our biggest dildo in rd4.
title: The Grappler(0-0)
